data.description: Brand new carpet in this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home on a corner lot. Open kitchen & dining area with bay windows overlooking the spacious backyard. This move in ready home features fresh neutral paint, a restyled fireplace, ceiling fans throughout, blinds, and a separate utility room with lots of storage. Good size pantry in kitchen as well. Spacious master bath & a built in vanity & full bath. Large storage building in back yard and separately fenced area for dog run or similar uses. Ample space to add a shop or RV Parking on the corner. Covered front entry way and covered backyard patio. Neighborhood is in the Canyon ISD. Short street on L-shaped cul-de-sac. All you need to do is move in!
